WEBVTT

00:03:58.877 --> 00:04:01.877 align:middle line:84%
Spice for the front page, isn't it?

00:04:01.877 --> 00:04:04.955 align:middle line:90%
All you can think of are
headlines for the front page.

00:04:04.955 --> 00:04:06.355 align:middle line:84%
Oh, drop it!

00:04:06.355 --> 00:04:21.815 align:middle line:84%
Here comes Judge Raghunath.

00:04:21.815 --> 00:04:26.698 align:middle line:90%
Such a gentleman! Why on earth
did that goon want to kill him?

00:04:26.698 --> 00:05:00.554 align:middle line:84%
Here comes your friend.

00:05:00.554 --> 00:05:03.895 align:middle line:90%
Is the jury in place?
- Yes, my Lord. Present.

00:05:03.895 --> 00:05:06.324 align:middle line:90%
Is the accused present?
- Present, my Lord.

00:05:06.324 --> 00:05:13.417 align:middle line:84%
Who is the counsel for the accused?

00:05:13.417 --> 00:05:19.130 align:middle line:84%
Who is the counsel for the accused?

00:05:19.130 --> 00:05:25.360 align:middle line:90%
Have you no lawyer
to defend your case?

00:05:25.360 --> 00:05:38.890 align:middle line:90%
In that case, the government...
- My Lord.

00:05:38.890 --> 00:05:47.966 align:middle line:84%
I'm the counsel for the accused.

00:05:47.966 --> 00:05:50.883 align:middle line:84%
I do not wish to defend myself.

00:05:50.883 --> 00:05:58.507 align:middle line:90%
I promised to defend you,
if you're ever arraigned. Remember?

00:05:58.507 --> 00:06:06.577 align:middle line:84%
Does the accused give his consent?

00:06:06.577 --> 00:06:09.842 align:middle line:84%
Yes.

00:06:09.842 --> 00:06:16.768 align:middle line:90%
Raj, you have been accused of
a murderous attack on Judge Raghunath.

00:06:16.768 --> 00:06:25.910 align:middle line:84%
You may plead your case.

00:06:25.910 --> 00:06:32.514 align:middle line:84%
I swear to speak the truth.

00:06:32.514 --> 00:06:37.970 align:middle line:90%
Judge Raghunath, can you tell us
why the accused tried to kill you?

00:06:37.970 --> 00:06:40.219 align:middle line:84%
Did he have any enmity with you?

00:06:40.219 --> 00:06:46.950 align:middle line:90%
Yes. The grudge that a born
felon bears...

00:06:46.950 --> 00:06:52.405 align:middle line:90%
against the judge who sentences
him and grants no reprieve.

00:06:52.405 --> 00:06:55.405 align:middle line:90%
Could there be no other reason
for such animosity?

00:06:55.405 --> 00:07:02.391 align:middle line:84%
None. How else could I relate to him?

00:07:02.391 --> 00:07:05.990 align:middle line:84%
I have no further questions.

00:07:05.990 --> 00:07:20.319 align:middle line:90%
Defense may proceed with
cross-questioning.

00:07:20.319 --> 00:07:24.281 align:middle line:84%
Judge, you are senior to me.

00:07:24.281 --> 00:07:29.888 align:middle line:90%
If in the course of questioning,
I happen to affront you do forgive me.

00:07:29.888 --> 00:07:34.380 align:middle line:90%
Someone's life is at stake.
And you have taught me...

00:07:34.380 --> 00:07:42.690 align:middle line:90%
to ignore all relationships for
the dispensation of justice.

00:07:42.690 --> 00:07:52.145 align:middle line:90%
This is my first interrogation.
Please give me your blessings.

00:07:52.145 --> 00:07:57.187 align:middle line:90%
What do you mean when you call
the accused a born felon?

00:07:57.187 --> 00:07:59.645 align:middle line:84%
He has been a tramp and a hoodlum...

00:07:59.645 --> 00:08:02.432 align:middle line:90%
ever since he was a child.
His record says it.

00:08:02.432 --> 00:08:07.121 align:middle line:90%
This penchant for crime has surely
been transmitted congenitally.

00:08:07.121 --> 00:08:09.144 align:middle line:84%
Judge, do you have any children?

00:08:09.144 --> 00:08:10.965 align:middle line:84%
No

00:08:10.965 --> 00:08:13.754 align:middle line:90%
But how is this question relevant
to this case?

00:08:13.754 --> 00:08:20.642 align:middle line:90%
Most relevant. Think again. Are you
certain that you have no children?

00:08:20.642 --> 00:08:25.789 align:middle line:90%
No. But I reiterate. This question...
- Can you recount the circumstance...

00:08:25.789 --> 00:08:30.210 align:middle line:90%
when you threw your wife
out of your house?

00:08:30.210 --> 00:08:35.256 align:middle line:90%
My Lord, am I to be forced to reply
to such meaningless questions?

00:08:35.256 --> 00:08:39.794 align:middle line:90%
Ms Rita, you may ask questions
relevant only to the case.

00:08:39.794 --> 00:08:43.491 align:middle line:90%
We wish to know whether or not,
the accused attempted murder.

00:08:43.491 --> 00:08:44.999 align:middle line:84%
If yes, then why?

00:08:44.999 --> 00:08:50.679 align:middle line:90%
Enough! Stop it! I'm a murderer!
Hang me if you will!

00:08:50.679 --> 00:08:52.509 align:middle line:84%
Order! Order!

00:08:52.509 --> 00:08:54.814 align:middle line:84%
Proceed with your questioning.

00:08:54.814 --> 00:08:58.859 align:middle line:90%
The accused does not deny having
assaulted Judge Raghunath.

00:08:58.859 --> 00:09:04.277 align:middle line:90%
But, as you said just now,
the question is why he did it.

00:09:04.277 --> 00:09:07.590 align:middle line:90%
This interrogation is meant
to reveal the answer...

00:09:07.590 --> 00:09:12.839 align:middle line:90%
if you my Lord, and Judge Raghunath
repose your trust in me for a while

00:09:12.839 --> 00:09:15.988 align:middle line:84%
You may proceed.

00:09:15.988 --> 00:09:19.749 align:middle line:90%
I repeat my question.
Can you recount the circumstance...

00:09:19.749 --> 00:09:23.969 align:middle line:90%
when you threw your wife
out of your house?

00:09:23.969 --> 00:09:28.510 align:middle line:90%
I beg your pardon, Judge Raghunath,
but this question is very important.

00:09:28.510 --> 00:09:31.400 align:middle line:90%
And not only for the accused.
For you too.

00:09:31.400 --> 00:09:36.162 align:middle line:90%
The cause of whatever is happening
today, lies rooted in your past.

00:09:36.162 --> 00:09:39.109 align:middle line:84%
Remember?

00:09:39.109 --> 00:09:41.374 align:middle line:84%
Remember?

00:09:41.374 --> 00:09:46.332 align:middle line:90%
Can you tell us? Why, when
and under what circumstance...

00:09:46.332 --> 00:09:49.499 align:middle line:90%
did you throw your wife
out of your house?

00:09:49.499 --> 00:09:52.259 align:middle line:84%
Why, when and under what circumstance...

00:09:52.259 --> 00:09:55.415 align:middle line:90%
..did you throw your wife
out of your house?

00:09:55.415 --> 00:09:57.957 align:middle line:84%
Why, when and under what circumstance...

00:09:57.957 --> 00:10:01.937 align:middle line:90%
