wife out of your house?

00:10:01.937 --> 00:10:03.489 align:middle line:84%
24 years ago...

00:10:03.489 --> 00:10:05.485 align:middle line:84%
I was practicing law in Lucknow.

00:10:05.485 --> 00:10:10.564 align:middle line:90%
I was the black sheep of the family,
because I opposed social norm...

00:10:10.564 --> 00:10:14.884 align:middle line:90%
and I had married a widow.
My father was a big gun.

00:10:14.884 --> 00:10:18.249 align:middle line:90%
And was away in Bombay most of the time.
He was unhappy with me.

00:10:18.249 --> 00:10:21.392 align:middle line:90%
But under no circumstance,
was I willing to leave Leela.

00:10:21.392 --> 00:10:25.683 align:middle line:90%
She was so good to me.
She was such a good woman.

00:10:25.683 --> 00:10:29.858 align:middle line:84%
And I was in love with her.

00:10:29.858 --> 00:10:33.316 align:middle line:90%
But once, on our way from
Kanpur to Allahabad...

00:10:33.316 --> 00:10:35.753 align:middle line:90%
