01:01:27.350 --> 01:01:30.507 align:middle line:90%
Aren't you ashamed? Give it to me.
Else, I'll beat you to pulp.

01:01:30.507 --> 01:01:33.262 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to kill you! Give me!

01:01:33.262 --> 01:01:40.941 align:middle line:84%
Where are you running away?

01:01:40.941 --> 01:01:46.794 align:middle line:84%
Give the purse!

01:01:46.794 --> 01:01:51.227 align:middle line:84%
You dare stare at me like that?

01:01:51.227 --> 01:02:06.210 align:middle line:84%
Hey... knife!

01:02:06.210 --> 01:02:09.290 align:middle line:84%
Are you running away? Coward!

01:02:09.290 --> 01:02:11.696 align:middle line:84%
Coward!

01:02:11.696 --> 01:02:18.640 align:middle line:84%
Scoundrel!

01:02:18.640 --> 01:02:21.750 align:middle line:84%
He ran away

01:02:21.750 --> 01:02:24.531 align:middle line:84%
Anyway, here's your purse"

01:02:24.531 --> 01:02:26.546 align:middle line:84%
Keep it.

01:02:26.546 --> 01:02:32.357 align:middle line:90%
You've been through so much
trouble for my sake.

01:02:32.357 --> 01:02:37.323 align:middle line:84%
No trouble. I've taken more.

01:02:37.323 --> 01:02:43.654 align:middle line:90%
I should apologise. You risked
your life to get my purse back.

01:02:43.654 --> 01:02:48.785 align:middle line:90%
And I suspected you.
- Not your fault.

01:02:48.785 --> 01:02:50.645 align:middle line:84%
It's just my looks.

01:02:50.645 --> 01:02:53.670 align:middle line:90%
Sometimes even the police
are mistaken.

01:02:53.670 --> 01:02:57.414 align:middle line:84%
Bye

01:02:57.414 --> 01:03:00.897 align:middle line:90%
How was the show?
- No use.

01:03:00.897 --> 01:03:04.310 align:middle line:90%
We'll find a car. Why worry?
Get over to the place.

01:03:04.310 --> 01:03:08.167 align:middle line:90%
I'll join you after a change
of clothes.

01:03:08.167 --> 01:03:11.250 align:middle line:90%
Hey Romeo! You tear your clothes
no sooner than you see a girl!

01:03:11.250 --> 01:03:34.915 align:middle line:90%
Get lost.
- Get going.

01:03:34.915 --> 01:04:30.640 align:middle line:84%
Stop! Thief!

01:04:30.640 --> 01:04:34.453 align:middle line:84%
Where are you going?

01:04:34.453 --> 01:04:36.778 align:middle line:84%
Inside.

01:04:36.778 --> 01:04:41.380 align:middle line:90%
Inside? What do you want?
- Strange question.

01:04:41.380 --> 01:04:43.911 align:middle line:90%
Your boss is the one who called me.
And you ask me what I want?

01:04:43.911 --> 01:04:46.580 align:middle line:84%
The boss, or the lady? Who called you?

01:04:46.580 --> 01:04:48.245 align:middle line:84%
Yes, the lady.

01:04:48.245 --> 01:04:51.620 align:middle line:90%
So you're the one
who fixes the piano?

01:04:51.620 --> 01:04:55.661 align:middle line:84%
Yes! The piano fixer!

01:04:55.661 --> 01:04:57.120 align:middle line:90%
Is the piano in there?
- Are pianos kept outside?

01:04:57.120 --> 01:05:23.837 align:middle line:90%
No! Inside. Come on in,
else I'll get into trouble.

01:05:23.837 --> 01:05:34.421 align:middle line:84%
Looks like a billionaire's palace!

01:05:34.421 --> 01:05:44.599 align:middle line:90%
Hello, darling.
- What did you say?

01:05:44.599 --> 01:05:47.772 align:middle line:84%
The mantle!

01:05:47.772 --> 01:05:51.524 align:middle line:84%
What a lovely mantle!

01:05:51.524 --> 01:05:57.802 align:middle line:84%
What a grand mansion!

01:05:57.802 --> 01:06:00.550 align:middle line:84%
The mantle!

01:06:00.550 --> 01:06:06.592 align:middle line:90%
What kind of a joke is this?
Here's the piano.

01:06:06.592 --> 01:06:09.666 align:middle line:90%
This piano is in bad shape.
Badly damaged.

01:06:09.666 --> 01:06:11.974 align:middle line:84%
Look.

01:06:11.974 --> 01:06:17.415 align:middle line:90%
Rotten! It'll take me time to fix it.
Go on, get back to work.

01:06:17.415 --> 01:06:41.696 align:middle line:84%
I'll fix it.

01:06:41.696 --> 01:06:47.415 align:middle line:84%
Who's playing my piano?

01:06:47.415 --> 01:06:58.999 align:middle line:90%
You?
- You!

01:06:58.999 --> 01:07:04.520 align:middle line:90%
I'm mistaken, once again
I thought it must be a thief.

01:07:04.520 --> 01:07:06.189 align:middle line:90%
That's what I am.
- What?

01:07:06.189 --> 01:07:09.832 align:middle line:90%
I mean, who else but a thief
would come in uninvited?

01:07:09.832 --> 01:07:12.981 align:middle line:84%
No, it's good of you to have come.

01:07:12.981 --> 01:07:17.361 align:middle line:90%
You did me a favour.
I should've called you over.

01:07:17.361 --> 01:07:22.473 align:middle line:90%
But I didn't know your address.
How did you find out my address?

01:07:22.473 --> 01:07:27.505 align:middle line:90%
What?
- How did you find out my address?

01:07:27.505 --> 01:07:30.691 align:middle line:90%
No, don't ask me that.
It's a secret.

01:07:30.691 --> 01:07:33.585 align:middle line:90%
Let's say, it's luck that has led me
to your doorstep.

01:07:33.585 --> 01:07:49.770 align:middle line:90%
Please be seated
- Thanks.

01:07:49.770 --> 01:07:52.729 align:middle line:84%
Cigarette?

01:07:52.729 --> 01:07:54.925 align:middle line:84%
Lighter?

01:07:54.925 --> 01:07:58.104 align:middle line:84%
No, thanks. Matches.

01:07:58.104 --> 01:08:01.333 align:middle line:90%
Madam, he's the piano-fixer...
- Piano fixer?

01:08:01.333 --> 01:08:03.837 align:middle line:90%
Your servant thinks I'm here
to fix the piano.

01:08:03.837 --> 01:08:10.768 align:middle line:90%
But you said...
- Never mind, take the call. Go on.

01:08:10.768 --> 01:08:15.594 align:middle line:90%
Strange fellow.
He took you for a piano mechanic.

01:08:15.594 --> 01:08:19.622 align:middle line:90%
Not his fault.
It's just my looks.

01:08:19.622 --> 01:08:22.362 align:middle line:84%
Inspector sahib, no thief came in here.

01:08:22.362 --> 01:08:24.127 align:middle line:84%
Please wait here.

01:08:24.127 --> 01:08:26.397 align:middle line:84%
Inspector?

01:08:26.397 --> 01:08:31.809 align:middle line:90%
What brings the police here?
Excuse me, I'll be back.

01:08:31.809 --> 01:08:38.151 align:middle line:90%
A car thief has sneaked into one
of the houses in this neighbourhood.

01:08:38.151 --> 01:08:43.781 align:middle line:90%
Have you seen anyone?
- No, no one came in here.

01:08:43.781 --> 01:08:48.585 align:middle line:90%
She's wrong about
no one coming in here.

01:08:48.585 --> 01:08:51.743 align:middle line:90%
I happen to be a visitor.
Would you be looking for me?

01:08:51.743 --> 01:08:54.252 align:middle line:84%
No... how could this be?

01:08:54.252 --> 01:08:58.676 align:middle line:84%
Okay. Forgive me.

01:08:58.676 --> 01:09:02.381 align:middle line:84%
Come.

01:09:02.381 --> 01:09:05.857 align:middle line:90%
Grand house.
- Yes. It belongs to the Judge.

01:09:05.857 --> 01:09:09.112 align:middle line:90%
Judge?
- Yes, he's my guardian.

01:09:09.112 --> 01:09:10.836 align:middle line:84%
Guardian?

01:09:10.836 --> 01:09:14.640 align:middle line:90%
Like the guard on the train
...signalling red and green?

01:09:14.640 --> 01:09:18.202 align:middle line:90%
No. After my father passed away,
I have been his ward.

01:09:18.202 --> 01:09:21.404 align:middle line:90%
For the sake of my education,
he left Lucknow and he came to Bombay.

01:09:21.404 --> 01:09:24.889 align:middle line:84%
I am much obliged to him.

01:09:24.889 --> 01:09:29.532 align:middle line:90%
Do judges sport such grand houses?
He must be making a pile on the side.

01:09:29.532 --> 01:09:32.761 align:middle line:90%
What a thing to say!
The judge is very principled.

01:09:32.761 --> 01:09:38.760 align:middle line:90%
He never spares criminals.
- I hope God spares him!

01:09:38.760 --> 01:09:45.437 align:middle line:90%
Not to worry. If you're ever arraigned
in his court, let me defend your case.

01:09:45.437 --> 01:09:51.553 align:middle line:90%
You... lawyer?
- Yes.

01:09:51.553 --> 01:09:55.353 align:middle line:84%
I took you for a schoolgirl.

01:09:55.353 --> 01:09:58.953 align:middle line:90%
That was a nice one. A couple
of months, and I'll be an advocate.

01:09:58.953 --> 01:10:02.454 align:middle line:84%
Would you like to see my degree?

01:10:02.454 --> 01:10:08.347 align:middle line:90%
A judge lives here. And a lawyer too.
Leaves only one to make a full court!

01:10:08.347 --> 01:10:11.452 align:middle line:90%
Yours truly. And here I am.
- And what are you up to?

01:10:11.452 --> 01:10:12.984 align:middle line:84%
I steal.

01:10:12.984 --> 01:10:16.362 align:middle line:90%
Stealing, picking pockets, locks,
ladies' purses, like yours...

01:10:16.362 --> 01:10:19.520 align:middle line:90%
that's what I'm up to.
- You're joking again. Be seated.

01:10:19.520 --> 01:10:24.184 align:middle line:90%
You don't think I'm a thief?
- No, I think you're a gentleman.

01:10:24.184 --> 01:10:27.840 align:middle line:84%
This is the new world order!

01:10:27.840 --> 01:10:31.414 align:middle line:90%
The thieves, the hoodwinkers, they
all dress in first class suits like...

01:10:31.414 --> 01:10:34.766 align:middle line:90%
...I'm wearing and
we take them for gentlemen.

01:10:34.766 --> 01:10:39.684 align:middle line:90%
But those who work hard for an
honest living and dress shabbily...

01:10:39.684 --> 01:10:45.351 align:middle line:90%
...are labelled tramps and wastrels.
The capitalists, the blackmarketeers...

01:10:45.351 --> 01:10:50.851 align:middle line:90%
the profiteers, the usurers...
who are they? Thieves, like I am!

01:10:50.851 --> 01:10:55.890 align:middle line:90%
You sound like a stock broker
or a banker.

01:10:55.890 --> 01:10:57.596 align:middle line:90%
You might say that give and take
of money is what I'm concerned with.

01:10:57.596 --> 01:11:00.992 align:middle line:90%
As far as banks are concerned,
I visit banks regularly.

01:11:00.992 --> 01:11:04.476 align:middle line:84%
Be seated.

01:11:04.476 --> 01:11:21.756 align:middle line:84%
Tell me your name.

01:11:21.756 --> 01:11:32.165 align:middle line:90%
Tell me, whose photo is this?
- Mine.

01:11:32.165 --> 01:11:36.422 align:middle line:90%
You?
- Yes, when I was young.

01:11:36.422 --> 01:11:39.526 align:middle line:84%
It's a birthday photo.

01:11:39.526 --> 01:11:50.329 align:middle line:90%
Your name?
- Rita. Why?

01:11:50.329 --> 01:11:55.476 align:middle line:90%
Ms Rita, would you like to come
to my house?

01:11:55.476 --> 01:11:59.531 align:middle line:90%
I'd like to show you
something unique.

01:11:59.531 --> 01:12:14.162 align:middle line:90%
My mother would be very pleased
to meet you. Come

01:12:14.162 --> 01:12:16.784 align:middle line:84%
Raj!

01:12:16.784 --> 01:12:18.526 align:middle line:84%
Rita!

01:12:18.526 --> 01:12:29.512 align:middle line:90%
You?
- After twelve years.

01:12:29.512 --> 01:12:32.767 align:middle line:84%
You've changed!

01:12:32.767 --> 01:12:38.750 align:middle line:84%
You haven't changed at all.

01:12:38.750 --> 01:12:42.489 align:middle line:84%
Where have you been, Raj?

01:12:42.489 --> 01:12:45.781 align:middle line:84%
Looking for you.

01:12:45.781 --> 01:12:49.369 align:middle line:90%
And at last, I've found you
- And when I saw you...

01:12:49.369 --> 01:12:52.260 align:middle line:84%
I took you for a thief.

01:12:52.260 --> 01:12:57.867 align:middle line:90%
Not your fault.
It's in my looks.

01:12:57.867 --> 01:13:44.797 align:middle line:84%
Raj!

01:13:44.797 --> 01:13:51.418 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:13:51.418 --> 01:14:08.589 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:14:08.589 --> 01:14:12.918 align:middle line:84%
"The heart had spoken to a heart."

01:14:12.918 --> 01:14:17.176 align:middle line:84%
"The heart had spoken to a heart."

01:14:17.176 --> 01:14:21.750 align:middle line:84%
"The old times have come back."

01:14:21.750 --> 01:14:25.792 align:middle line:84%
"The old times have come back."

01:14:25.792 --> 01:14:31.836 align:middle line:90%
"He brought the happiness with
him, my heart flutters."

01:14:31.836 --> 01:14:48.801 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:14:48.801 --> 01:14:53.136 align:middle line:90%
"From the eyes, he dwelled
in my heart."

01:14:53.136 --> 01:14:57.355 align:middle line:90%
"From the eyes, he dwelled
in my heart."

01:14:57.355 --> 01:15:01.256 align:middle line:84%
"I smile and scatter the stars."

01:15:01.256 --> 01:15:05.819 align:middle line:84%
"I smile and scatter the stars."

01:15:05.819 --> 01:15:12.600 align:middle line:90%
"Feelings dance and sing,
my heart flutters."

01:15:12.600 --> 01:15:29.500 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:15:29.500 --> 01:15:33.298 align:middle line:90%
"The days belong to us
and love is young."

01:15:33.298 --> 01:15:37.689 align:middle line:90%
"The days belong to us
and love is young."

01:15:37.689 --> 01:15:41.544 align:middle line:90%
"My world is flourishing
due to him."

01:15:41.544 --> 01:15:46.600 align:middle line:90%
"My world is flourishing
due to him."

01:15:46.600 --> 01:15:52.291 align:middle line:90%
"The thief returned to my heart,
my heart flutters."

01:15:52.291 --> 01:15:58.783 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:15:58.783 --> 01:16:06.138 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:16:06.138 --> 01:16:10.552 align:middle line:84%
The Judge is here.

01:16:10.552 --> 01:16:13.177 align:middle line:84%
So here you are. And you're late.

01:16:13.177 --> 01:16:18.940 align:middle line:90%
The doctor has told you to come home
and rest for at least an hour.

01:16:18.940 --> 01:16:21.827 align:middle line:90%
But you won't listen.
You look so tired.

01:16:21.827 --> 01:16:23.670 align:middle line:90%
Hello, Rita.
- Hello, Rita!

01:16:23.670 --> 01:16:28.754 align:middle line:90%
Just sit here. I'll get you
your dressing gown.

01:16:28.754 --> 01:16:31.427 align:middle line:90%
Tell me, where have you been
all this time?

01:16:31.427 --> 01:16:36.599 align:middle line:90%
I had a lecture in the law college.
I went there directly from the court.

01:16:36.599 --> 01:16:40.795 align:middle line:90%
All that jabbering
is giving me a headache.

01:16:40.795 --> 01:16:46.277 align:middle line:90%
That's bound to happen. The doctor
told you to eat before eight.

01:16:46.277 --> 01:16:50.587 align:middle line:84%
It's nine thirty now.

01:16:50.587 --> 01:16:56.829 align:middle line:90%
Listen to that!
Even the clock is angry with you.

01:16:56.829 --> 01:17:17.564 align:middle line:84%
Come on.

01:17:17.564 --> 01:17:22.599 align:middle line:90%
Tell me about yourself. What have
you been up to all evening?

01:17:22.599 --> 01:17:29.362 align:middle line:90%
You look as if you've found
a treasure.

01:17:29.362 --> 01:17:33.545 align:middle line:90%
You could say that. A long-lost friend
is no less than a treasure.

01:17:33.545 --> 01:17:44.337 align:middle line:90%
You'll be glad when you meet Raj.
You're certain to like him!

01:17:44.337 --> 01:17:52.171 align:middle line:90%
Who is this Mr. Raj? Where does he live?
What does he do? What's his family name?

01:17:52.171 --> 01:17:57.139 align:middle line:90%
He's a childhood friend.
We were in school together.

01:17:57.139 --> 01:17:59.912 align:middle line:84%
I'm seeing him after twelve years!

01:17:59.912 --> 01:18:03.762 align:middle line:84%
After twelve years?

01:18:03.762 --> 01:18:06.450 align:middle line:90%
After so many years,
most people change.

01:18:06.450 --> 01:18:10.293 align:middle line:90%
Raj has changed too. At school,
he used to be very quiet.

01:18:10.293 --> 01:18:13.635 align:middle line:90%
Now he has great sense of humour.
When I asked him what he's up to...

01:18:13.635 --> 01:18:16.795 align:middle line:84%
he said he's a thief.

01:18:16.795 --> 01:18:21.754 align:middle line:90%
Maybe that wasn't a joke?
- I don't follow you.

01:18:21.754 --> 01:18:24.545 align:middle line:84%
Never mind.

01:18:24.545 --> 01:18:27.676 align:middle line:90%
You know what young men
are like, these days.

01:18:27.676 --> 01:20:06.390 align:middle line:90%
Who knows, they might steal
something valuable.

01:20:06.390 --> 01:20:10.501 align:middle line:90%
The water is deep.
You might drown.

01:20:10.501 --> 01:20:17.566 align:middle line:90%
Not without you
- Is that so? Try that.

01:20:17.566 --> 01:20:37.766 align:middle line:84%
Is that so?

01:20:37.766 --> 01:20:40.124 align:middle line:90%
Hey lady, haven't you finished
dressing yet?

01:20:40.124 --> 01:20:44.387 align:middle line:90%
Where are you headed?
Gentlemen don't barge in...

01:20:44.387 --> 01:20:48.751 align:middle line:90%
when ladies are changing dresses.
Don't you know that?

01:20:48.751 --> 01:20:58.793 align:middle line:84%
How would I know?

01:20:58.793 --> 01:21:07.221 align:middle line:90%
I'm no gentleman.
- Savage.

01:21:07.221 --> 01:21:10.780 align:middle line:84%
Savage.

01:21:10.780 --> 01:21:17.418 align:middle line:90%
I'm not about to give in
to your type.

01:21:17.418 --> 01:21:20.843 align:middle line:84%
Where are you running away?

01:21:20.843 --> 01:21:25.500 align:middle line:90%
Let go of my hand. What kind
of a stupid joke is this?

01:21:25.500 --> 01:21:26.399 align:middle line:84%
You savage!

01:21:26.399 --> 01:21:29.157 align:middle line:90%
Am I?
- Yes! You're a savage!

01:21:29.157 --> 01:21:32.562 align:middle line:90%
Savage?
I'm a penniless, uneducated tramp!

01:21:32.562 --> 01:21:34.864 align:middle line:84%
I don't fit into high society!

01:21:34.864 --> 01:21:37.459 align:middle line:90%
How dare I maul your fragile body
with my beastly hands.

01:21:37.459 --> 01:21:39.751 align:middle line:90%
I told Ma that childhood friends,
like childhood days are gone...

01:21:39.751 --> 01:21:43.125 align:middle line:84%
never to return.

01:21:43.125 --> 01:21:47.787 align:middle line:84%
Good of you to have told me my class.

01:21:47.787 --> 01:21:51.228 align:middle line:84%
It was a joke. Don't get angry.

01:21:51.228 --> 01:22:02.530 align:middle line:84%
You want to hit me? Go ahead.

01:22:02.530 --> 01:22:06.150 align:middle line:84%
Whom will I hit?

01:22:06.150 --> 01:22:08.648 align:middle line:84%
You?

01:22:08.648 --> 01:22:40.875 align:middle line:84%
Or myself?

01:22:40.875 --> 01:22:45.819 align:middle line:84%
Hey! Hey!

01:22:45.819 --> 01:22:48.836 align:middle line:84%
Are you happy?

01:22:48.836 --> 01:22:51.907 align:middle line:84%
No.

01:22:51.907 --> 01:22:56.685 align:middle line:90%
Where are you lost?
- Up there

01:22:56.685 --> 01:23:00.898 align:middle line:90%
Come back.
- Where to?

01:23:00.898 --> 01:23:05.378 align:middle line:90%
Beside me.
- Why?

01:23:05.378 --> 01:23:16.232 align:middle line:84%
No reason.

01:23:16.232 --> 01:23:22.172 align:middle line:84%
Aren't you ashamed?

01:23:22.172 --> 01:23:27.883 align:middle line:90%
What are you looking at?
The Moon?

01:23:27.883 --> 01:23:32.308 align:middle line:84%
No. Clouds.

01:23:32.308 --> 01:23:35.118 align:middle line:90%
What's your problem?
You don't see the Moon...

01:23:35.118 --> 01:23:40.868 align:middle line:90%
and you see the dark clouds?
Won't you tell me?

01:23:40.868 --> 01:23:44.695 align:middle line:84%
Who else can I tell?

01:23:44.695 --> 01:23:47.618 align:middle line:90%
Rita.
- Yes.

01:23:47.618 --> 01:23:50.450 align:middle line:90%
We're seeing each other
after twelve years.

01:23:50.450 --> 01:23:52.385 align:middle line:84%
So what?

01:23:52.385 --> 01:23:57.268 align:middle line:90%
A lot changes in twelve years.
